#: /Users/rikdekker/Documents/Development/IntraVox/specialAppInfoFakeDummyForL10nScript.php:3
msgid "SharePoint-style intranet pages for Nextcloud — no code required"
msgstr ""

#: /Users/rikdekker/Documents/Development/IntraVox/specialAppInfoFakeDummyForL10nScript.php:4
msgid ""
"IntraVox transforms Nextcloud into a full-featured intranet platform. Build "
"professional pages with a visual drag-and-drop editor — no coding required. "
"A complete, open-source alternative to SharePoint.\n"
"\n"
"**Page editor:**\n"
"* Drag-and-drop widget placement with flexible grid layouts (1–5 columns)\n"
"* 7 ready-made page templates to get started quickly\n"
"* Collapsible sections, sticky toolbar, and row duplication\n"
"* Draft/Published workflow with page locking to prevent conflicts\n"
"\n"
"**Rich widget library:**\n"
"* Text (with tables and markdown), images, video, links, files, dividers\n"
"* Calendar widget with multi-calendar merged view and recurring events\n"
"* People widget with user profiles, filters, and birthday tracking\n"
"* News widget with list, grid, and carousel layouts\n"
"* Photo Story widget — photo galleries with EXIF metadata, OpenStreetMap "
"location clustering, and an accessible Apple-style lightbox\n"
"* File Story widget — document libraries with timeline, list, tiles, and "
"grouped layouts; MetaVox-aware filtering; federated-share awareness\n"
"\n"
"**Collaboration & engagement:**\n"
"* Emoji reactions and threaded comments on pages\n"
"* Version history with one-click restore\n"
"* Personal RSS feed for following page updates\n"
"* Public sharing with optional password protection\n"
"\n"
"**Content management:**\n"
"* Multi-language support — admins choose which Transifex-translated "
"languages to enable\n"
"* Navigation editor with megamenu and sidebar options\n"
"* Full export/import to ZIP — including Confluence HTML import\n"
"* Demo content to get started in minutes\n"
"\n"
"**Enterprise ready:**\n"
"* Department-based access control via GroupFolders ACL\n"
"* Nextcloud Unified Search integration (Ctrl+K)\n"
"* Seamless theming, users, groups, and files integration\n"
"\n"
"**Requirements:**\n"
"* Nextcloud 32, 33, or 34\n"
"* PHP 8.2 or higher\n"
"* GroupFolders app (installed and enabled)\n"
"\n"
"**Ideal for:**\n"
"* Company intranets and news portals\n"
"* Department knowledge bases\n"
"* Internal communication and documentation\n"
"* SharePoint-to-Nextcloud migrations"
msgstr ""

